title: Native Instruments - Action Strikes [Kontakt]
description:
SEED WHEN YOU FINISH DOWNLOADING!

ACTION STRIKES is a radically innovative instrument for huge cinematic percussion. Its state-of-the-art workflow delivers maximum impact with unmatched versatility.

    Add huge cinematic percussion to your tracks
    Direct the drama with real-time control
    Create full arrangements from time-tested rhythms

- Open your latest Kontakt
- Go to Libraries tab
- Click add library
- Select the directory/folder that you downloaded at.
- On Win user, just Yes or Accept when prompted to add libary.
- Mac user, read www.native-instruments.com/en/support/knowledge-base/show/794/
(Except WITHOUT the key or serial part!)
- The added library will show up on the left panel.
